26amp;crop=0%2C5.9300064808814%2C100%2C88.139987038237\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25612704/AirPods42.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C5.9300064808814%2C100%2C88.139987038237\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e$169\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe fancier version of the new AirPods 4 offer support for active noise cancellation, a wireless charging case that can use either Qi or Apple Watch pads, and a speaker in the case that chirps to help you find it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eAt its \u003ca href=\"https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series-10-airpods\"\u003eSeptember 2024 event\u003c/a\u003e, Apple introduced the AirPods 4, a pair of wireless earbuds available in two variations: a $129 standard model and a $179 noise-canceling model. Both versions represent significant upgrades over the third-gen AirPods, with a more comfortable design and improved audio performance. They’re also better for taking calls thanks to Apple’s Voice Isolation feature, which focuses the mics on your voice so that you can more clearly be heard in noisy environments.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe $179 AirPods 4 with Active Noise Cancellation offer a surprisingly effective noise cancelling mode, a helpful transparency mode, and several other Pro-level features. The AirPods Pro still do a better job of tuning out noise, but the AirPods 4 with ANC still do a good job of reducing sound. They also offer other perks formerly reserved for Apple’s top-of-the-line earbuds, including wireless charging and a case with a built-in speaker that allows you to easily track it down via Apple’s Find My app. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAlthough they only just launched a few months ago, we’re already starting to see discounts on both versions of the AirPods 4. You can now buy the standard AirPods 4 for $117 ($12 off) at \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGHMNQ5Z?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003eAmazon\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8836598/type/dlg/https://www.staples.com/apple-airpods-4-wireless-ambient-sound-earbuds-with-usb-c-charging-case-4th-generation-bluetooth-white-mxp63ll-a/product_24616046\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003eStaples\u003c/a\u003e. The AirPods 4 with Active Noise Cancellation are on sale for around $168.99 ($11 off) at \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Headphones-Cancellation-Transparency-Personalized/dp/B0DGJ7HYG1/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003eAmazon\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8836598/type/dlg/https://www.staples.com/apple-airpods-noise-canceling-earbuds-with-usb-c-charging-case-4th-generation-bluetooth-white-mxp93ll-a/product_24616047?cid=ps:gs:dot:nb:pla:transtech\u0026amp;gad_source=1\u0026amp;gclid=CjwKCAiA5pq-BhBuEiwAvkzVZeVSa69-HGcNmTJfOARsbDPw5vcezQASrLD-2ZBFGakma67AQICYmRoCHaQQAvD_BwE\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003eStaples\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1852457-REG%2Fapple_mxp93ll_a_airpods_4_with_active.html%2F%3Fap%3Dy%26ap%3Dy%26smp%3Dy%26smp%3Dy%26store%3D420%26lsft%3DBI%253A5451%26gad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCjwKCAiA5pq-BhBuEiwAvkzVZRfhACk2JhAphZqZYN_NZv9nhWdf2oxc-wtv4Kni6rnq69AXQtDABxoCT2EQAvD_BwE\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003eB\u0026amp;H Photo\u003c/a\u003e, which is $20 shy of their all-time low.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"Iewbkw\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eThe best AirPods Pro (second-gen) deals\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-product-filter=\"\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Cancellation-Transparency-Personalized-High-Fidelity/dp/B0D1XD1ZV3/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\